## **Prompt recommendations**

* Use coherent natural language to describe the **subject + action + environment**. If aesthetics matter, include descriptors of **style,** **color,** **lighting,** or **composition**. For details, see [Seedream 4.0-4.5 prompt guide](/docs/ModelArk/1829186).
* Keep text prompts under 600 English words. Very long prompts may scatter the information, causing the model to overlook details and focus only on key points, which can result in missing elements in the generated image. 

